name: Keyboards
description: This Keyboard Enthusiast Mystery Box is filled with all sorts of parts, components, and tools that every mechanical keyboard lover will love to use! Past boxes have offered items like switch openers, switch lube, switch trays, mousepads, and deskmats. Boxes can also offer switches, keycaps, custom coiled cables, and more!

name: Dungeons & Dragons
description: Dungeons and Dragons also known as fantasy tabletop role-playing game. You can enjoy it by playing with your friends, add minatures to your collection or simply show off to your friends. In this mystery box there can be items ranging from Dice Sets to Mini Figures and even to game maps that can bring your game to life

name: Arts & Crafts
description: Arts and Crafts box! Mystery box is filled with traditional and modern arts and crafts. If you are into knitting, painting and Pintrest pins this mystery box is for you! Save time from buying individual parts, this box comes with the DIY kits ready to go!

name: Gardening
description: Gardening mystery box! If you are indoor or outdoor plant lover, we have the right plants for you. Our mystery box includes plants, seeds and tools for all your garden needs.
